{"tid":1808555,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［回帶］麥當勞講大話　賣出170噸黑心肉","createTime":"2020-01-02T12:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T03:02:52.000Z","uid":78819,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3d1321daea894265d3889c6140214c3cb186f1","tid":1808555,"uid":78819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】香港麥當勞爆出疑用「黑心肉」醜聞。食物安全中心踢爆麥當勞講大話，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麥當勞去年至今先後兩次從上海福喜購入脆辣雞腿及吉列豬塊，市民最少把約170公噸懷疑黑心肉落肚。</span></span>該中心叫停所有內地福喜食品輸港，即時禁售並封存福喜進口食品。麥當勞推搪是發放訊息混亂而致歉，承認另有10種食材來自河北及廣州福喜。<br />\n記者：陳沛冰　陳凱迎　溫婉婷　王家文　林偉聰<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：停售聲明與網頁不符<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食物安全中心踢爆麥當勞講大話，指麥當勞去年至今先後兩次從上海福喜購入脆辣雞腿及吉列豬塊。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n內地揭發上海福喜食品有限公司將過期及發霉肉加工，供應內地麥當勞等多間連鎖食肆。香港麥當勞本周一曾聲稱沒任何食品是來自上海福喜，但由網民貼圖踢爆後，即改口指有向美國福喜集團採購，但並非來自上海福喜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140725/18811582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140725%2F18811582&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPj%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=95827851\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140725%2F18811582&h=31c463b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140725/18811582</a>"},{"pid":"4833846bc6ad8b6198719001392d0e701f1447db","tid":1808555,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvGpqyx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvGpqyx.gif&h=9b425962&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc968afae575b8ad6aa85df0c2fff043edb596aa","tid":1808555,"uid":78819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"仲食支那落肚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\